WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:04.000
The Barclays app. How to make payments.

2
00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:09.400
The Barclays app puts the power
to pay at your fingertips.

3
00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:13.560
Just log in and choose, 'Pay & Transfer'.

4
00:00:14.320 --> 00:00:17.560
Select 'Pay a recent or new payee'.

5
00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:21.800
Choose the account you
would like to pay from

6
00:00:24.840 --> 00:00:28.440
and then tap 'Add / select payee'.

7
00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:34.320
If you're paying someone you've paid
before, either through the app or online banking

8
00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:37.160
just select their name
from the list.

9
00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:41.760
Or to pay someone new, choose
'Add new payee'.

10
00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:44.240
Tap 'Enter bank details'.

11
00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:47.840
Choose who you're paying

12
00:00:48.160 --> 00:00:51.080
and enter their information.

13
00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:56.000
Once you've added all the details, we'll
check them with the recipient's bank

14
00:00:56.200 --> 00:01:00.880
if the details match, we'll
confirm the details are correct.

15
00:01:01.080 --> 00:01:05.560
If the name doesn't match
other responses may occur.

16
00:01:05.760 --> 00:01:10.760
You can search 'Confirmation of payee' on the
Barclays website for more information.

17
00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:15.160
If the details match, tap 'Continue'.

18
00:01:15.920 --> 00:01:20.120
Next, enter the amount you want to pay
and add a reference that you'll both see

19
00:01:20.120 --> 00:01:21.400
on your statements.

20
00:01:21.400 --> 00:01:23.360
Then choose whether this is a one off

21
00:01:23.360 --> 00:01:27.760
payment or a standing order
and select 'Review payment'.

22
00:01:27.960 --> 00:01:31.040
Choose the type of payment you're making.

23
00:01:31.040 --> 00:01:35.040
Tap to confirm you've read the information
about fraud and scams

24
00:01:35.360 --> 00:01:37.720
and if you're happy tap 'Continue'.

25
00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:40.840
If you're paying someone new,

26
00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:46.880
you'll need your debit card as you'll need
to add a few more details for security.

27
00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:52.400
Check the details, tap 'Confirm payment'
and you're done.

